Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:16.72,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be3\fad(150,200)}身躯冻得通红
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:25.35,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be3\fad(150,200)}心灵在黑暗中成长
